description: This Chainlink VRF top 5% score Sakura purrs with a rating of 49, and a multiplier of 5x. It has a total score of 245, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Stringalong for North, 2 for East, 8 for South, and Leverage for West. Sakura has the personality suit of whale. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
